<sect1 id="dir_d7d61354c43df5b3f9e499bdacf27dcd_1autotoc_md211">
<title>helios::engine::runtime</title><para>Runtime infrastructure for game execution, world management, and lifecycle orchestration.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_d7d61354c43df5b3f9e499bdacf27dcd_1autotoc_md212">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides the core runtime components that manage game execution. It includes world state management, messaging infrastructure for commands and events, object pooling for efficient memory reuse, and the game loop orchestration system.</para>
</sect1>
